{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just went there to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I read since there was about 480 people together in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the British marched in, that was about half.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm telling a lie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was 100,000 left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By the end of the day, they found survivors where they reckoned was only 15-- 16,000 men and 17,000 women survived after-- from the whole caboodle after the war, from 480,000 people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, only 18 months ago, I went to the British Museum where-- where they had a special day for Belsen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were some of the soldiers who actually liberated us, and we had a-- a nice day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A nice day there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The memories flooding back, and telling us how by accident they found Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was only that one tank somehow got lost on the way that they come across this Belsen-- this camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And things were so-- they were telling, and I knew about it because I read in books since.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I experienced it, mostly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Things were so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had to take my string off from my trousers to hold up my trousers, tie me and another guy, or another-- another boy-- tie our string to dead bodies' feet, because they had two wheeled carts and they couldn't cope to drag him about 100, 200 yards, to this great big hole they-- they--",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mass graves.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And throw them in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- everybody was assigned because they tried to hide everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a terrible thing to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the time you got there, the bit of flesh they had on their body was rubbed away by us dragging them all these-- as I said, I don't know whether it was 100 yards, 200, 300, 500.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
